luding of one or two bits that didn\'t end up in the finished product, and not only from this movie), concept art and previsualization. It goes into doing a sequel and without the original director to boot, turning a first person perspective written work into something that has to show things the protagonist doesn\'t see and do without narration, the differences between it and the first one, designs, location shooting(one set was built on an unused floor of an operating hotel!), acting(Malone\'s passion paid off!), bringing back those who made the earlier entry great, costumes and make-up, the water scenes, stunts(the spin was real!), Hawaii, post, sound and VFX. Yup, there\'s some of the usual lovefest. Thankfully, most of it is earned.There is some disturbing content in this. I recommend this to anyone who wants to learn more about how this was put together. 8/10','145 min','Documentary','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYmYyZGY3ZGItODY2YS00NWI1LTgwYzctNDlmMjhmZDc1YjdlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTEyMDcwNw@@._V1_SX300.jpg','14 Nov 2013'),('tt4083246','Surviving the Zombie Apocalypse with Rick and Ed','2014–','series',NULL,NULL,NULL,'N/A',NULL),('tt4116068','Alfred Alfer','2006–','series',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOGVhMWRlYjUtOGRiMy00NzAzLTkzODktNDBjMTVmNTQ0YWM5XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzAxNzExMDM@._V1_SX300.jpg',NULL),('tt4116284','The Lego Batman Movie','2017','movie',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTcyNTEyOTY0M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTAyNzU3MDI@._V1_SX300.jpg',NULL),('tt4131766','Mission: 4Count','2014–','series',NULL,NULL,NULL,'N/A',NULL),('tt4145286','The Hunger Games: Mockingjay - District Voices','2014–','series','Lions Gate and Google team up to present \"District Voices\". A five episode series describing what each of the districts- 2,5,6,8,9 do to help the Capitol. Some of your favorite youtubers will make a special appearance such as, iJustine, Feast of Fiction, ThreadBanger and more. Tune into the YouTube channels to